<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٤٠٠ - ٤٧٧ هـ)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٠٠٩ - ١٠٨٤ م)</span><a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
